columns.name: route_table_id
columns.description: Contains the ID of the route table.

columns.name: owner_id
columns.description: The ID of the AWS account that owns the route table.

columns.name: associations
columns.description: Contains the associations between the route table and one or more subnets or a gateway.

columns.name: routes
columns.description: A list of routes in the route table.

columns.name: propagating_vgws
columns.description: A list of virtual private gateway (VGW) propagating routes.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: A list of tags that are attached to the route table.
